 <strong>Type of contract:<br></strong><br> </div> <div>We offer a Full time position.<br><br> </div> <div>Apply by sending your CV to jobs@nftstudios.io<br><br> </div> <div><br></div> <div>—--------------------------------------------------------------<br><br> </div> <div> <strong>About the company: <br></strong><br> </div> <div>NTF Studios is a group of companies that share a mission: <strong>To Build the Metaverse, one block at a time.</strong> We are a team of over 60 people working remotely from all over the world, developing innovative digital products, tools, and technologies to enable the NFT and Metaverse spaces to grow and thrive. <br><br> </div> <div>By leveraging Blockchain technology, we empower companies, communities, and users to start their own web3 businesses, build a strong presence in the Metaverse, create their own products, explore their creativity, and engage in new and fascinating digital experiences.<br><br> </div> <div>Take a look at our web: https://www.nftstudios.io/<br><br> </div> <div> <br><br> </div> </div> When applying, mention the word CANDYSHOP to show you read the job post completely.]]></description>
