<description><![CDATA[<p>We are looking for someone to initiate, develop and execute foundational DeFi strategic initiatives for the Flow ecosystem to establish it as a key contender in the blockchain ecosystem. This is an entrepreneurial role and ideal candidate needs to demonstrate they have operated at the intersection of Product Management &amp; Business Development with a strong focus on financial &amp; liquidity principles.</p><br><p><strong>What We'll Accomplish Together</strong></p><br><ul> <li>Develop, lead &amp; execute the overall DeFi business strategy for Flow, including product development, partnerships, and business development.</li> <li>Increase the visibility of Flow within the TradFi and Mining/Staking community.</li> <li>Lead with the best security practice and standards. Ensure the steady growth and safe-run of their business from hacks and financial attacks.</li> <li>Provide expertise for Flow Foundation treasury management in partnership with the CFO.</li> <li>Monitor and analyze DeFi market trends, competitive landscape, and developer feedback to optimize our product offerings.</li> </ul><br><p><strong>A Litte About You:</strong></p><br><ul> <li>Bachelor's degree in finance, economics, or a related field.</li> <li>Strong understanding of DeFi protocols, smart contracts, and blockchain technology.</li> <li>Proven track record of launching and scaling successful DeFi products.</li> <li>Strong leadership and team management skills.</li> <li>Excellent communication, collaboration, and problem-solving skills.</li> <li>Ability to work in a fast-paced, dynamic environment and adapt to changes quickly.</li> <li>Passion for decentralization, blockchain technology, and financial inclusion.</li> </ul><br><p><strong>More about Flow:</strong></p><br><p>Flow is the layer 1 blockchain for builders. Flow blockchain is designed for a new generation of consumer apps, games, and the digital assets that power them. Flow helps developers build the kinds of applications people want to use, focusing on consumer-friendly onboarding and the ability to handle mainstream scale. The Flow team is a humble and curious bunch of builders, scientists, marketers and product experts who share a passion for blockchain technology and the new kinds of software it enables. Our people are our greatest strength: our diverse team flourishes in an environment where personal autonomy and professional growth are encouraged.</p><p></p> When applying, mention the word CANDYSHOP to show you read the job post completely.]]></description>
