nance.</em></div> <div> </div> <div><em>Please find our UK/EU Applicant Privacy Notice and our California Applicant Privacy Notice for reference.</em></div> </div> <p></p> </div> When applying, mention the word CANDYSHOP to show you read the job post completely.]]></description>
