<description><![CDATA[<p><strong>About Staking Rewards</strong></p> <p>Staking Rewards is on a mission to make Staking safe and easy. We are 20 people who operate a website that is used by 250,000 people every month and an API that is used by Bloomberg, Binance, Coinbase, etc.</p> <p>We are backed by some of the world's best investors ( i.e. Galaxy Digital, Coinshares, Digital Currency Group).</p> <p>We are now at a crucial stage in our journey as the activity in staking is exploding. There are a ton of challenges facing us to unlock massive growth for Staking Rewards. However, with the right mindset, strategy, and the world-class team that we’re building, we know we can push forward.</p> <p>This Role is fully remote but limited to GMT +/- 3.</p> <p></p> <p></p> <p><strong>Our Expectations for the Role</strong></p> <ul> <li>Lead user growth efforts/campaigns for stakingrewards.com (I.e. SEO, Co-Marketing, Content etc)</li> <li>Lead the creation of compelling and authentic stories around our products</li> <li>Lead the written and visual content output on all media (newsletter, youtube, twitter, reddit)</li> <li>Grow the brand perception of Staking Rewards from a well-established niche project to a global fintech giant</li> </ul> <p></p> <p><strong>What we offer</strong></p> <ul> <li>You will be responsible for driving 100,000s of new users to a growing player in the crypto/fintech space </li> <li>You will be responsible for 100,000s of new users to discover the simplicity to gain agency over their investments and earn passive income with crypto</li> <li>You get a unique opportunity to drive bold growth efforts and experiment fast with a well established, and differentiated brand in the crypto space</li> <li>We are young, flexible, and agile. If you are dedicated and eager to learn - you will make a real difference at Staking Rewards over the years to come.</li> <li>We pay top-of-the-market salaries for high-achievers.</li> </ul> <p></p> <p></p> <p><strong>What your Profile could look like</strong></p> <ul> <li>Track-Record in driving at least 1000 Subscribers/Follower/Sign-Ups for any project (e.g. SM account or website)</li> <li>In-Depth Understanding of DeFi/Staking</li> <li>Journalistic Experience</li> <li>Strong SEO Experience</li> </ul> <p></p> <p><strong>How to apply</strong></p> <p>No lengthy process, just submit your social accounts (Twitter, LinkedIn, personal website) here. We're looking forward to hearing from you.</p> <p></p> When applying, mention the word CANDYSHOP to show you read the job post completely.]]></description>
